<div class='row'>
  <p class='small-12 large-centered columns, intro'>
    Avoid asking yourself the question everyone secretly wants
    to know.
  </p>
</div>
<div class='row'>
  <p class='small-12 large-centered columns, intro'>
    "How many days can I eat this without dying?"
  </p>
</div>
<div class='row'>
  <p class='small-12 large-centered columns, intro' id='last-p'>
    Find recipes, inspiration, and eat something that doesn't come
    out of a crinkly, brightly colored bag.
  </p>
</div>
<span class='hidden'>
  Hey, you! Yes, you, the one poking around my site. Are you sneaking around
  because you're interested in hiring me? Perhaps it's time to check out
  the div below.
  <div>
    <%= link_to "My Github", "https://github.com/moonpastry" %>
  </div>
</span>
<div class='form'>

  <%= form_tag recipes_path do %>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='small-12 large-centered columns, search-box' >
      <%= text_field_tag :search, params[:search], :method => 'post' %>
      <%= hidden_field_tag :page, 1 %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- <div class='row'> -->
    <div class='small-6 columns'>
      <%= submit_tag 'Search' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<% end %>
